Value.value: I need strapping adventurers like you to recover some lore for me.
I'm trying to discern the nature of the Mylocks.
Mynocks? What on Toril is a Mynock? This is fascinating stuff! Thank you!
Their lair should be near the center of the hills. Don't worry if you can't find it, they've been fortifying their walls lately.
I'm still digging through those tablets you brought back, thanks again.
Can you get to their lair and see if there's any lore on their origins?
I'll, of course, pay you handsomely!
